{"tid":2087812,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"安達臣道直幡 「國安惡法 自由被壓」","createTime":"2020-06-30T23:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T02:39:44.000Z","uid":50386,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a991fc15241052350ff945b8760f7e03bcfa05f8","tid":2087812,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T23:36:40.000Z","msg":"港版國安法於回歸23周年前一小時正式生效，政府昨晚深夜才發出港版國安法全文，涉及危害國家安全的四大罪名涵蓋廣泛。清晨約6時，秀茂坪安達邨謙達樓對上山坡，打橫掛上一條直幡，黑底白字寫有「國安惡法 自由被壓」，至於旁邊另一條懷疑直幡，則被強風吹疊，未能看到寫上甚麼。飛行服務隊直升機亦一度於直幡上空盤旋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200701/ZX2XPSLJG556KU2XH7CLZGKASQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200701%2FZX2XPSLJG556KU2XH7CLZGKASQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwK7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=b3fe5769\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200701%2FZX2XPSLJG556KU2XH7CLZGKASQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=2a26538a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200701/ZX2XPSLJG556KU2XH7CLZGKASQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"dd44235b4e1ebbcffd8e1e6d00a133bb8fa1a29c","tid":2087812,"uid":18477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T23:38:19.000Z","msg":"打橫即係明喻壽終正寢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce09b9dc163830c08065997de5e15b71991643c3","tid":2087812,"uid":94613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T23:40:21.000Z","msg":"<del>唔掛之5點幾比直直直嘈醒左仲要停左5分鐘</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=